title: Pictures: NASCAR's Hollywood Casino 400 at the Kansas Speedway
text:
Joey Logano took the checkered flag at the Hollywood Casino 400 at the Kansas Speedway. He clipped Matt Kenseth late in the race, spinning out the No. 20. 
Logano already advanced to the next round of NASCAR's Chase with a win last week in Charlotte.
